NoiseBouquet — Notices and Attributions
========================================

NoiseBouquet is a fork of Befaco's Noise Plethora (VCV Rack edition),
ported to the Expert Sleepers Disting NT module format. It is distributed
under GPL-3.0 (see LICENSE).

The following components are vendored or derived from upstream projects.
Their original copyright headers are preserved in-source and remain in force.


1. Noise Plethora algorithms
----------------------------
Files:    algos/P_*.hpp, algos/NoisePlethoraPlugin.hpp (NT-adapted),
          algorithm structure and DSP graph topologies.
Source:   Befaco / Noise Plethora (Eurorack module + VCV Rack adaptation).
Authors:  Norman Goldwasser (original Teensy hardware), Befaco team
          (Eurorack + VCV Rack adaptation), and contributors.
License:  GNU General Public License v3.0.


