3. VCV Rack runtime shim
------------------------
Files:    include/rack.hpp, nt_rack_shim.cpp/.hpp.
Source:  Re-implementation (not vendored) of the small subset of the VCV
         Rack 2 API (`rack::dsp::RingBuffer`, `APP->engine->getSampleRate()`)
         that the Noise Plethora algorithms call into. No code is copied
         from VCV Rack. Behaviour is observable-equivalent.
License: GPL-3.0 (matches enclosing project).


